"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></div>\r\n          <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n          <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: lisu\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">产品的简介：</span></span></div>\r\n          <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: lisu\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">  健力宝运动饮料，富含碱性电解质、天然蜂蜜、不含咖啡因，具有以下功效：<br />   酸碱平衡身体好——含碱性电解质，促进体内酸碱平衡，帮助消除疲劳，快速恢复体力<br />   蜂蜜滋润身体好——添加天然蜂蜜，含多种营养成分，滋养身体<br />   气足劲爽身体好——“气”可促进电解质的快速补充，快速恢复体力</span></span></div>\r\n          <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n        </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n          <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"> <img style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 10px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"alt\" src=\"/images/upload/Image/20130809120600093159767.jpg\" /> \r\n            <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n