m: 10px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 753px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/23px ''arial helvetica sans-serif''; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); overflow: hidden; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 10px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n    <div style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 753px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">生产工艺：--自古好的奶茶就是“打”出来的。打奶茶的核心工艺是均质技术。形象的说，就是茶和奶在高压均质机中被高速剪切、高速撞击，和类似爆炸效应的空穴作用下，使颗粒得到超微细化，唯有如此，才能创造立体顺滑的口感和浓郁香气。<br />口感描述：--顺滑、柔滑、柔和、饱满、浓郁、厚实、厚重、有料感、有层次、立体感强、茶香足、奶味真实、茶香与奶香和谐、风味浓郁、香味纯正、回味佳。</div>\r\n  </div>','images/201312/thumb_img/8595_thumb_G_1470993821.jpg','images/201312/goods_img/8595_G_1417827764.jpg','images/201312/source_img/8595_G_1473282978.jpg','1','','0','1','0','0','1387001382','0','1','1','0','0','0','10.0','0','1446967523','0','','0.00','-1','-1','0','0','0','','0','0','0.00');");
